title: Stock price of Goldman Sachs 2004 to 2019
summary: In general Stock price in U.S. dollars has rose over the Year.

Stock price in U.S. dollars is roughly constant from 2009 to 2010, slightly decreasing from 2010 to 2011, gradually increasing from 2011 to 2013, roughly constant from 2013 to 2015, and lastly slightly increasing from 2015 to 2016.
The steepest decrease occurs in between the Year 2010 and 2011.
Maximum Stock price in U.S. dollars, about 239.45 was reported at Year 2016
The lowest Stock price in U.S. dollars, of value 90.43 was reported at Year 2011
